            "body": "This proposal looks quite confusing. I think what is required here is:\r\n1. A way to change how CSI sequences are handled in terminal. This only seems possible to implement for sequences not recognized by libvterm. The `XM` capability of `xterm-256colors` is not one of them as libvterm recognizes the first argument `1006` but ignores the second argument `1000`. https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/21106#issuecomment-1573096660\r\n2. A way to force enable mouse forwarding in terminal. This should be easy to implement.",
